:"Are you available for emergencies on weekends and holidays?","answer":"Absolutely. We offer 24/7 emergency plumbing service, including weekends and holidays. Burst pipe at 2 AM on Christmas? We'll be there."},"q4":{"question":"What areas do you serve in the GTA?","answer":"We serve the entire Greater Toronto Area including Scarborough, North York, Etobicoke, Markham, Mississauga, Brampton, and surrounding communities within a 50 km radius."},"q5":{"question":"Are your plumbers licensed and insured?","answer":"Yes. All our plumbers are fully licensed and insured in Ontario. We carry comprehensive liability insurance for your peace of mind."},"q6":{"question":"Do you offer any warranties on your work?","answer":"Yes. All our work comes with a satisfaction guarantee. If you're not happy with the results, we'll make it right at no extra charge."}},"nav":{"quote":"Quote","services":"Services","about":"About","reviews":"Reviews","testimonials":"Testimonials","contact":"Contact"},"footer":{"rights":"All rights reserved.","privacy":"Privacy Policy","terms":"Terms of Service"}}